<h2 id="typed-arithmetic-expressions-toy-typed-language">Typed Arithmetic Expressions (Toy Typed Language)</h2>

<p>The toy lang from <code class="highlighter-rouge">SmallStep</code> is too â€œsafeâ€ to demonstrate any <strong>runtime (or dynamic) type errors</strong>.  â€“ è¿è¡Œæ—¶ç±»å‹é”™è¯¯
So thatâ€™s add some operations (common church numeral ones), and <code class="highlighter-rouge">bool</code> type.</p>

